# WebSocket

Message shapes and field names → [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

## Server (`apps/server`)

- Validate with Zod, errors from `constants/errors.ts` (`errors.INVALID_*`)
- Delegate calculation to `@nasa-fuel/fuel-core`
- Respond on every message; check `socket.readyState` before send

## Client (`apps/client`)

- Persistent connection; reconnect on disconnect
- Send updated payload on every input change
- Handle `{ error: string }` and `{ totalFuel, breakdown }` responses

No REST submit endpoint.
